      "originalText": "\n- Fonts\n        - Redaction\n        - Queens by Kilotype\n\n- Each photo has a short description like a museum\n\n- Front page will be like a photography book cover\n\n- Palette will be paper-like:\n        - Tool: https://www.figma.com/tools/ \n        - Off-white for background (#F2F0EF)\n        - ",
